race.comment: PRICKLY POPPY (9) improved nicely last start at Murray Bridge when rising to this trip. Now fourth-up and fitter again, she'll be charging late and looks one of the key dangers. SANIKA (1) took a solid step forward second-up when ridden more prominently. Strips fitter, draws well, and has further improvement to come. ZIGGY STARCRAFT (3) hasn't won for quite some time but is knocking on the door and only needs to hold his form to be very competitive. Win won't shock. LADY LUPARA (8) was a determined winner two back at Murray Bridge but less effective last time. Gets in well with the claims and there's no reason she can't return to the winner's circle this time.
